      <div class="scroll-animate max-w-[1500px] mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16 px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-8">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia leading-tight">
            Heal your <span class="text-brand-gold">mind</span>, <span class="text-brand-gold">body</span>, and <span class="text-brand-gold">soul</span>
          </h2>
          
          <div class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-dark font-gotham leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>
              Our program is designed to <strong>accelerate self-discovery</strong> and provide guests with the tools needed to understand and integrate their transformative experiences.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              <strong>Ceremonies with ancestral plant medicine</strong> are complemented by modern practices such as <strong>yoga, breathwork, meditation, Hemy-Sync</strong> and integrative workshops that deepen the healing process.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-base opacity-70">
              Our retreats are held regularly, offering flexibility so you can join when it best fits your schedule.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="pt-4">
            <a href="/casa-del-jaguar-way" class="inline-block bg-brand-dark text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg shadow-xl font-gotham uppercase tracking-wide hover:bg-brand-gold hover:text-brand-dark transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
              Discover the Journey
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
          <img src="/img/ayahuasca-cabeza-clava.webp" alt="Ancestral Medicine - Cabeza Clava" class="w-full max-w-lg md:h-[600px] object-cover rounded-md shadow-black shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#fdf6e7] to-[#fdf9f1] scroll-animate relative overflow-hidden">
      
